	   <tr><td colspan=2>Have 3 guild enchanters with these in offhand and tash / malo a hard mob.  Then have the 3 chanters chain click this while melee kill it.  Sure for a single party item the effect is rather useless, but you have to realize that free mana is always good.  People give the donal's bp a hard time too but as a shaman I can just cann down every few mobs and get complete healed for mana.  Every click item has its advantages and disadvantages.  More advantages than not I'd say, considering you can duck to interrupt spells now.<br><br>Stun spells are resisted about as much as root spells, but free mana ownz and you all know it. =P<br><br>I click my bracer, pegasus cloak, staff, etc. and I love it.<br>&nbsp;<br>Mandicus Lifescourge - Oracle  / Zakani - Disciple / Sleezard - Meatslab / Summan - Necro -Innoruuk</td></tr>
